title: Wall Street Breakfast: The Week Ahead
author: Seeking Alpha
dc:creator: Seeking Alpha
description: Symbotic (SYM), an AI-powered robotic software company already working with retail giants like Walmart (WMT), could be going public. Athletic wear company Lululemon (LULU) is due to report earnings this week and Morgan Stanley is calling it a compelling opportunity. The latest installment of Top Gun is here, and the box office is still falling short of pre pandemic revenues.
